						               													<description>&amp;quot;Pirate Adventure Game. These is a very simple game for play on beach or in backyard, with plastic toy soldiers. The focus is on a fast-action game, easy to learn and easy to play. Our game is for small battles, only - with forces of 100 men or less on each side.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are fourteen types of characters specified in the rules. These include pirates (&amp;quot;the heroes of our game&amp;quot;), tow militia, the Navy, Marines, Moors, Conquistadors, Privateers, Indians, South Pacific Natives, and Samurai.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are seven types of ranged weapons specified in the rules: Long Rifle, Pistol, Musket, Bow, Cannon, Light Cannon, and thrown weapons (spear, hatchet, tomahawk, marlinspike, etc.) Each weapon is rated for range, damage, and rate of fire.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Concepts covered in the rules include boarding, prisoners, ports, treasure, and the effect of tides and wind on boats. Campaign suggestions are also included.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One of the Jersey Shore Battle Games, available for free online&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
